| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4555 — Recovery Inhibition (qiulong)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 649f8fc4-2e7b-5a4d-8d2e-8b77ca087b33"
